ay]] |date=1 April 2002}}</ref>\n|-\n|2002 || ''[[Humraaz]]''|| {{nts|2,200,000}}\n| rowspan=\"6\" | <ref name=\"boi00s\">{{cite web|title=Music Hits 2000-2009 (Figures in Units)|url=http://boxofficeindia.com/showProd.php?itemCat=286&catName=MjAwMC0yMDA5|website=[[Box Office India]]|date=5 February 2010|url-status=dead|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100205042845/http://boxofficeindia.com/showProd.php?itemCat=286&catName=MjAwMC0yMDA5|archivedate=5 February 2010}}</ref>\n|-\n|2003 || ''[[Tere Naam]]''|| {{nts|3,000,000}}\n|-\n|2004 || ''[[Veer-Zaara]]''|| {{nts|3,000,000}}\n|-\n|2005 || ''[[Aashiq Banaya Aapne]]''|| {{nts|2,000,000}}\n|-\n|2006 || ''[[Kabhi Alvida Naa Kehna]]''|| {{nts|2,000,000}}\n|-\n|2007 || ''[[Om Shanti Om]]''|| {{nts|1,900,000}}\n|-\n|2008 || ''[[Ghajini (2008 film)|Ghajini]]'' || {{nts|1,900,000}} || <ref name=\"boi00s\"/>\n|-\n|2010 || ''[[Dabangg]]'' || {{nts|1,000,000}} || <ref name=\"puli\"/>\n|-\n|2011 || ''[[Rockstar (2011 film)|Rockstar]]''|| {{nts|1,000,000}} ||\n|-\n|2012 || ''[[Cocktail]]''|| {{nts|1,000,000}} ||\n|-\n|2013 || ''[[Aashiqui 2]]''|| {{nts|1,000,000}} ||\n|-\n|2014 || ''[[Ek Villain]]''|| {{nts|1,000,000}} ||\n|-\n|2015 || ''[[Bajirao Mastani]]''|| {{nts|1,000,000}} ||\n|-\n|2016 || ''[[Ae Dil Hai Mushkil]]''|| {{nts|1,000,000}} ||\n|-\n|2017 || ''[[Jab Harry Met Sejal]]''|| {{nts|1,000,000}} ||\n|-\n|2018 || ''[[Padmaavat]]''|| {{nts|1,000,000}} ||\n|-\n|2019 || ''[[Kalank]]''|| {{nts|1,000,000}} ||\n|-\n|}\n\n==Album streams==\n{{See|List of most-viewed Indian music videos on YouTube}}\n\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" | Year\n! scope=\"col\" | Soundtrack\n! scope=\"col\" | Composer(s)\n! scope=\"col\" | Lyricist(s)\n! scope=\"col\" | [[YouTube]] streams {{small|(billions)}}\n! scope=\"col\" | {{Abbr|Ref|Reference(s)}}\n|-\n| [[List of Bollywood films of 2017|2017]]\n| ''[[Tiger Zinda Hai]]''\n| [[Vishal\u2013Shekhar]]\n| [[Irshad Kamil]]\n| 1.6\n| <ref>{{cite web |title=Tiger Zinda Hai 